    EOAssert
    This class is the entry point for writing assertions to WebObjects related unit tests.

Package com.wounit.matchers Description

This package contains the Matcher classes and the EOAssert class that works as an entry point to write unit test for Enterprise Object related logic. The EOAssert class has the required assertion methods and matchers that can be used for this task.
Since:
1.0
